history.content: If you actually go to the link as written, as opposed to just clicking on the link, you'll find the listing.

I still didn't see anything that way, but I found a lot of them by going to the current course lists from the main EECS page, looking under Courses

and then looking under Spring 2017 for EE and CS.  The decals are listed as sections of 198.  I also found one more by searching on the main

page for decal: https://people.eecs.berkeley.edu/~jpduarte/resources/DeCalCourseHardwareMakers.pdf

Have a great weekend!

Heather

EECS Grad Advisor and one of the few who incessantly checks e-mail over the weekend...
